    "description": "On a rainy night, Yuseong wakes up alone among piles of garbage. With no memory of who he is or where he came from, he begins a new life working at Café Noah.\n\nThough his days are peaceful, they are also precarious - until Kim Woohyun, the owner of a hardware store, appears. With a seemingly indifferent yet piercing gaze, he watches Yuseong’s every move, exuding an air of danger.\n\nWhat Yuseong assumes is a fleeting encounter turns into something more when Woohyun saves him from an attack, and surprises him with unexpected words:\n\n“Don’t we know each other? You don’t remember?”  \n“Do you want to be friends?”\n\nYuseong, numb to his own wounds, and Woohyun, who persistently probes the trembling emotions beneath them, begin a connection. What will the two of them discover at the end of this night?\n\n[Original Webtoon](https://ridibooks.com/books/4624000075) ",
